<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 8: TIMING GEAR TRAIN AND FRONT COVER -
        FRONT COVER, REAR HALF - INSTALLATION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>INSTALLATION</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new crankshaft gear and oil spline gear, if required. Install the crankshaft,
                refer to
                <emph type="bold">"Section 7"</emph>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install front cover (rear half) as follows:</para>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Install a new front cover O-Rings and gaskets into the grooves in the cover (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600822">8.22</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Mount the rear half of the front cover to the crankcase using nine bolts. Tighten the
                    bolts to the special torque value (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600823">8.23</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step2>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Refer to
                <emph type="bold">"Section 5"</emph>
                for installing the camgear or camgear and camshaft assembly.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Check camshaft end play and be sure the tappets move freely in their bores.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <figure id="ef1600822" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg7234" filename="../figeg7/eg7234.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 8.22 Rear Half Front Cover Gasket Location</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">1. Gasket</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">2. Front Cover</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">3. Crankcase</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1600823" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5330" filename="../figeg5/eg5330.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 8.23 Installing Rear Half Of Front Cover To Crankcase</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
